messages.content: What is ComfyUI-SizeFromPresets?
ComfyUI-SizeFromPresets is a custom node for ComfyUI that adds nodes to output the width and height of the selected size from presets.
How can you install ComfyUI-SizeFromPresets?

To install ComfyUI-SizeFromPresets, navigate to the custom_nodes directory in your ComfyUI installation and clone the repository using the command: git clone https://github.com/nkchocoai/ComfyUI-SizeFromPresets.git
What does the 'Size From Presets (SD1.5)' node do?

The 'Size From Presets (SD1.5)' node allows you to select image size presets for SD1.5. It outputs the width and height of the selected size. The presets can be configured from the presets/sd15.csv file.
What is the purpose of the 'Empty Latent Image From Presets (SD1.5)' node?

The 'Empty Latent Image From Presets (SD1.5)' node lets you select image size presets for SD1.5. It outputs an empty Latent Image and the width and height of the selected size. The presets can be set from the presets/sd15.csv file.
How does the 'Random ... From Presets (SD...)' node function?

The 'Random ... From Presets (SD...)' node randomly selects a preset from the CSV file. If it's a Size node, it outputs the width and height of the selected size. If it's a Latent Image node, it outputs an empty Latent Image and the width and height of the selected size.
What does the 'Get Similar Resolution' node do?
The 'Get Similar Resolution' node selects a resolution from the presets that is closest to the input image size. It outputs the width and height of the selected size.
What is the function of the 'Get Similar Resolution Empty Latent' node?

The 'Get Similar Resolution Empty Latent' node chooses a resolution from the presets that is nearest to the input image size. It outputs an empty Latent Image and the width and height of the selected size.
What is ComfyUI-SizeFromPresets?
ComfyUI-SizeFromPresets is a custom node for ComfyUI that adds nodes which output width and height of the size selected from a preset.
How can you install ComfyUI-SizeFromPresets?
To install ComfyUI-SizeFromPresets, navigate to the custom_nodes directory in your ComfyUI installation and run the command: git clone https://github.com/nkchocoai/ComfyUI-SizeFromPresets.git
What does the 'Size From Presets (SD1.5)' node do?
The 'Size From Presets (SD1.5)' node allows you to select image size presets for SD1.5 and outputs the width and height of the selected preset. Presets can be set from the presets/sd15.csv file.
What is the purpose of the 'Empty Latent Image From Presets (SD1.5)' node?

The 'Empty Latent Image From Presets (SD1.5)' node selects image size presets for SD1.5 and outputs an empty latent image, width, and height of the selected preset. Presets can be set from the presets/sd15.csv file.
What does the 'Get Similar Resolution' node do?
The 'Get Similar Resolution' node selects a resolution close to the input image size from the presets and outputs the width and height of the selected preset.
How does the 'Random ... From Presets (SD...)' node function?

The 'Random ... From Presets (SD...)' node randomly selects from the presets listed in the CSV file. For Size, it outputs the width and height of the selected preset. For Empty Latent Image, it outputs an empty latent image, width, and height of the selected preset.
What is the purpose of the 'Get Similar Resolution Empty Latent' node?
The 'Get Similar Resolution Empty Latent' node selects a resolution close to the input image size from the presets and outputs an empty latent image, width, and height of the selected preset.
